 about 6. The others are at most mildly relativistic. The\ngalaxies are not off-axis versions of the powerful quasars, but Cygnus A might\nbe an exception.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Nov 2006 20:58:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
